public class WaterSurfaceType
extends _WaterBoundarySurfaceType

Type describing the surface of a water body, which separates the water from the air. As subclass of _CityObject, a WaterSurface inherits all attributes and relations, in particular an id, names, external references, generic attributes and generalization relations.
